Kitchen
The kitchen is the location where coffee was made at 2pm.<SEP>The kitchen is where John Smith entered and made coffee.

John
John is a person seen in the kitchen making coffee at 2pm and wearing a blue shirt.

Sarah
Sarah talked with John Smith about the upcoming project deadline and mentioned needing to finish the quarterly report by Friday.

John Smith
John Smith entered the kitchen wearing a blue shirt at 2:30 PM.

Blue Shirt
A blue shirt worn by John Smith.

Coffee
Coffee made by John Smith in the kitchen.

Upcoming Project Deadline
The deadline for the upcoming project discussed by John Smith and Sarah.

Quarterly Report
A quarterly report that Sarah needs to finish by Friday.

Friday
The day by which the quarterly report must be finished.

Conference Room
The location where John Smith and Sarah agreed to meet tomorrow at 10 AM.

Meeting
A meeting scheduled for tomorrow at 10 AM in the conference room between John Smith and Sarah.

2:30 PM
The time when John Smith entered the kitchen.

10 AM
The scheduled time for the meeting tomorrow.

Tomorrow
The day after the current entry when the meeting is scheduled.

SPK_0012
Speaker identified as SPK_0012 who asks where an item was sourced “我上哪搞上上去的？” during a coding session.<SEP>Speaker identified as SPK_0012 who asked a Mandarin question about where something was placed while working at a desk.

SPK_0013
Speaker identified as SPK_0013 who said “我感觉。” and “这个延迟。” while at a dual‑monitor workstation.

SPK_0014
Speaker identified as SPK_0014 who uttered “三十来。” and later “已经奔着。” during a workspace recording.

SPK_0015
Speaker identified as SPK_0015 who asked “四十秒去的？” while a white cat was present on the desk.

SPK_0016
Speaker identified as SPK_0016 who contributed to a transcription mentioning a model.

TEMP_SPEAKER_01
Temporary speaker referenced alongside SPK_0016 in a transcription about a model.

SPK_0017
Speaker identified as SPK_0017 who discussed a repetition and an original version in Mandarin.

SPK_0019
Speaker identified as SPK_0019 who said “他是.” while the workspace was shown.

SPK_0020
Speaker identified as SPK_0020 who mentioned “三十秒左右” and later said “就是.”.

Dual-Monitor Setup
A workstation configuration with two monitors used across multiple scenes for coding and file management.

Desk
The desk surface that holds all items such as models, bottles, hard drive, and microphone arm.

Model Airplane
A generic model airplane present on several desk setups.<SEP>A small model airplane placed on the desk in the workspace.

Colorful Circular Object
A colorful circular decorative object on the desk.<SEP>A colorful circular decorative item observed on the desk.

Essential Oil Bottles
Small bottles containing essential oils positioned on the desk.

Hard Drive
An exposed hard drive located on the desk.

Microphone Arm
A boom arm holding a microphone used by several speakers.<SEP>A microphone arm situated on the desk.

White Cat
A white cat seen resting on the desk in several scenes.

White Dog Figurine
A small white model dog figurine placed on the desk.

Circular Digital Device
A circular digital device observed on the desk.

Plain Wall
The plain wall serving as the background behind the desk.

Curved Monitor
A curved monitor used in later entries showing code and text files.<SEP>A curved monitor that is part of the dual‑monitor workstation.

Flat Monitor
A flat monitor that is part of the dual‑monitor workstation.

macOS Dock
The macOS Dock UI element displayed on one of the monitors.

Code Editor
The code editor application shown on the main screen of the workstation.

File Manager
The file manager program displayed on a secondary monitor.

Code/Text Editing
The activity of coding and text editing displayed on the monitors.

Circular Green-Patterned Object
A circular object with a green pattern observed on the desk.

Circular Artwork
A circular artwork piece placed on the desk.

Unknown Male
An unidentified male voice that greets someone in an indoor office setting.

Unknown Female
An unidentified female voice commenting on the nice weather while looking outside.

SPK_0001
Speaker identified as SPK_0001 who says “我的电信。 不しな。” in a desk setup containing a monitor, figurine, and model airplane.

SPK_0002
Speaker identified as SPK_0002 who says “hello. hello.” while testing audio in a desk setup.

SPK_0003
Speaker identified as SPK_0003 who asks “can you hear me?” with no visible person present.

SPK_0006
Speaker identified as SPK_0006 who asks “自己在说什么？” while recording with a microphone at a tech‑focused desk.

SPK_0008
Speaker identified as SPK_0008 who asks “做呢？” in a workspace with dual monitors and tech gear.

SPK_0009
Speaker identified as SPK_0009 who discusses lag with the phrase “你感觉好慢？ 他延迟。” while using dual monitors.

SPK_0010
Speaker identified as SPK_0010 who expresses frustration about delay with “延迟感觉。 很长。”

SPK_0011
Speaker identified as SPK_0011 who questions “不知道为什么？” while working on code.

Indoor Office Setting
An indoor office environment featuring a desk where greetings and weather comments occur.

Window View
A view through a window showing a sunny day with trees, observed by the unknown female speaker.

Desk Setup
A workstation desk containing monitors, figurines, model airplanes, and various tech accessories.

Samsung Monitor
A Samsung brand monitor displaying data tables, code, or spreadsheets in multiple entries.

White Fox Figurine
A white figurine of a fox placed on the desk.

Air France Model Airplane
A model airplane branded with Air France displayed on the desk.

White Electronic Device With Dial
A small white electronic device featuring a dial, partially visible on the desk.

Partial CD Drive
A partially visible CD drive component on the desk.

Circular Map‑Like Object
A circular decorative object resembling a map, located on the desk.

Exposed Hard Drive
An exposed hard drive component visible on the desk.

Dual Monitors
Two monitors positioned side‑by‑side displaying code or documents.

Small Bottles
Small bottles placed on the desk.

Patterned Container
A patterned container on the desk.

Cables
Tangled cables visible behind the desk.

Data Table
A data table displayed on the Samsung monitor in the desk setup.

List Interface
A list interface shown on the Samsung monitor during audio testing.

Spreadsheet/Chat
A spreadsheet or chat view displayed on the Samsung monitor in later entries.

Code Document
Code or document content displayed on dual monitors or curved monitor.

Wall
The plain wall background visible behind the desk setups.

Planet‑Like Decorative Object
A circular decorative object resembling a planet on the desk.
